RE Participation App is the essential private companion for real estate investors seeking to qualify for Real Estate Professional Status (REPS) or Material Participation. We built RE Participation App with a "privacy-first" philosophy. Your financial data, property details, and activity logs are yours alone—stored securely in your personal iCloud, not on our servers.

Key Features:
* Private & Secure: No account creation required. All data is encrypted and synced directly through your personal iCloud account. We never see, sell, or store your data.
* Unlimited Evidence: Upload unlimited photos, receipts, and documents to substantiate your logs. Keep your audit trail robust without worrying about storage limits.
* Effortless Logging: Quickly add logs for any property. Use the Live Activity timer on your Lock Screen to track site visits in real-time.
* Progress Dashboard: Stay on top of your hour goal with clear visual breakdowns by property and activity type.
* Audit-Proof Exports: Generate comprehensive CSV reports that bundle your logs with all your attached evidence photos and receipts—ready for your CPA.

Take control of your tax strategy securely with RE Participation App.


